1
00:01:08,239 --> 00:01:10,599
Are you sure you won't call the cops on us?

2
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,760
I promise.

3
00:01:12,599 --> 00:01:13,719
Mom.

4
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:15,159
I'm begging you.

5
00:01:15,159 --> 00:01:16,879
Just let them go.

6
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,400
Please, I'm begging you.

7
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,480
Damn it.

8
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:25,000
I'm out of cigarettes.

9
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,400
What's the deal with Li Yao?

10
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:26,920
Huh?

11
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,120
He's dragging his feet.

12
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:33,000
Right.

13
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,920
The boss has been gone a while too,

14
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:36,480
with no word from him.

15
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:38,200
Hope nothing went wrong.

16
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:40,239
What was the boss thinking, anyway?

17
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:41,079
He kidnaps someone,

18
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:42,120
and brings them to this scenic spot.

19
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:44,239
He's been watching too many dramas.

20
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,480
Worried the cops can't find us,

21
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,519
or here to enjoy the view?

22
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,079
Enjoy the view, my ass.

23
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:49,400
If you ask me, you're

24
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,879
the prettiest view around here.

25
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,200
It's my first time here,

26
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,040
in such a beautiful place.

27
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:56,760
Might as well enjoy the view.

28
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,359
Enough.

29
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:58,200
Now I'm a kidnapper.

30
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,120
Shut your mouth.

31
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,599
Hey.

32
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,479
Could they be in there?

33
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,039
You go distract them.

34
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:14,520
I'll call the police.

35
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,520
Okay.

36
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,800
Hello, is this 110?

37
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:27,680
I'm here.

38
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:30,879
You guys can go.

39
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,360
How come you came alone?

40
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:34,919
It's no big deal.

41
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,960
I can handle it alone.

42
00:02:36,719 --> 00:02:38,560
There's a mother and two kids in there.

43
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:39,759
Can you really handle them alone?

44
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,520
No, I gotta call the boss to confirm.

45
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,319
Stop them!

46
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:58,879
Li Yao.

47
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,400
So you're betraying us, huh?

48
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:01,439
Old Xia.

49
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:02,680
You can't keep making mistakes.

50
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,039
Honey.

51
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,800
Daddy.

52
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,280
No one's at Xiaohui's place,

53
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:10,960
and her phone's unreachable.

54
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,560
Xiao Yifan's phone is unreachable too.

55
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:14,280
Could something have actually happened?

56
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:18,360
I'm such a piece of trash.

57
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,719
Don't get worked up, calm down.

58
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:21,560
You just lie here quietly.

59
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,120
Hurry.

60
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,120
Quick, call Chairman Zheng.

61
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:25,960
Hurry!

62
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:26,680
Okay.

63
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,240
Don't get worked up, I'll call him.

64
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:34,520
Kidnapping women and kids? That's pathetic.

65
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,719
If you've got the guts, come at me!

66
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:38,800
You're the one who brought them here.

67
00:03:39,439 --> 00:03:40,319
Li Yao.

68
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,800
You traitor.

69
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:44,759
Yang Hui.

70
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:45,919
Take the kids and go first.

71
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:51,120
You're not going anywhere!

72
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:09,599
Xiao Yifan

73
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,599
I'll kill you!

74
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,920
Li Yao!

75
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,000
Li Yao!

76
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:31,639
Ah!

77
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:33,560
Honey!

78
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,600
Daddy!

79
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:43,279
Run!

80
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,839
Li Yao!

81
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:48,920
Hang in there!

82
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,199
We're going to the hospital right now!

83
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,639
Family members, wait outside.

84
00:05:28,639 --> 00:05:29,600
Fang Bing.

85
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,720
Let me tell you something.

86
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,240
You're nothing but a fool.

87
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,480
I should have given birth to a rock instead of you.

88
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,879
Hit-and-run, kidnapping.

89
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,079
Look at what you've done.

90
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:40,079
Any one of them is enough to put you away.

91
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:40,839
You hear me?

92
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,360
Don't ever call me again.

93
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,279
Tell your wife to get a lawyer, fast.

94
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,319
How much money do you have left?

95
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:01,319
Wire it to me, right now.

96
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:02,959
Money, money, money!

97
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,199
How could I have any money left?

98
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,839
What about the five million I wired you?

99
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,680
The general contract for Plot 7, Phase One,

100
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,360
have you sealed the deal?

101
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,639
You're nothing but bad luck.

102
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,519
Ever since I've been with you,

103
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:15,560
I haven't had a single happy day.

104
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,519
I'm bad luck?

105
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:19,800
Like you're any better!

106
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,800
Why are you packing in the middle of the night?

107
00:06:22,199 --> 00:06:23,000
Have you done something

108
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,920
shady again?

109
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,319
Are you trying to skip town?

110
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,240
Get out of my way!

111
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:50,959
Bing.

112
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:51,720
Bing, honey.

113
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,600
What are you doing here?

114
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,519
What's wrong?

115
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,079
Grab all the cash in the house.

116
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:04,040
Come with me and Lay low.

117
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,800
What's going on, Bing?

118
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:07,800
What happened?

119
00:07:09,879 --> 00:07:10,519
Stop asking.

120
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,199
You're better off not knowing.

121
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,839
Hurry up and pack.

122
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:19,959
My stomach is upset.

123
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:21,079
Maybe you should go on your own.

124
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,439
You don't want to come with me?

125
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:26,600
Haven't I treated you well all these years?

126
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:29,199
Bing.

127
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,240
Our son needs regular prenatal checkups.

128
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:32,560
I can't be running around everywhere.

129
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:34,040
Don't worry.

130
00:07:34,319 --> 00:07:35,240
I'll take care of myself.

131
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:37,759
Fine.

132
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,759
Get me one million in cash.

133
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:41,160
The rest is for you and our son.

134
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,920
One million?

135
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:44,879
The money's all in fixed deposits.

136
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:47,079
Where would I withdraw it this late at night?

137
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,000
Bing.

138
00:07:49,439 --> 00:07:50,279
What happened?

139
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:51,519
Did you kill someone or what?

140
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,879
Cut the crap.

141
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:53,759
Go get the money, now.

142
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:56,639
There's no money at home.

143
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:58,439
What did you say?

144
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,319
I gave you millions in cash.

145
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,800
Now you tell me there's no money?

146
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,720
Is it because my business is failing?

147
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,800
You want to Find a richer man?

148
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,480
Or are you

149
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:06,680
and that Boss Wang

150
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,560
sleeping with each other too?

151
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:09,399
Answer me!

152
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,040
Bing.

153
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:12,319
Bing.

154
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,199
Mr. Fang!

155
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,160
Get up!

156
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:23,839
Ah!

157
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,720
Stealing my man,

158
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,319
and spending my family's money!

159
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,720
She's carrying my child.

160
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:37,559
Fang Bing!

161
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:39,279
You really are a bastard.

162
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,159
Have you no conscience?

163
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,519
Su Yuanyuan.

164
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,759
I've put up with you long enough.

165
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,919
This is my home.

166
00:08:50,159 --> 00:08:50,879
Get out!

167
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:51,759
Get out!

168
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,639
Your home?

169
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,799
This was bought with my family's money.

170
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,159
How is it suddenly yours?

171
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:57,679
Enough!

172
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,440
I'm in trouble.

173
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,799
I have to skip town right now.

174
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,600
Which of you has money on hand?

175
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:09,600
Get it ready for me.

176
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,120
Look at the pathetic state of you.

177
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,200
What kind of trouble could you possibly cause?

178
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:19,399
All you do is run, run, run.

179
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:21,039
Where would you even run to?

180
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:22,639
Let me tell you.

181
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,240
He Junjie getting hit by a car...

182
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,720
I was the one who ordered Li Yao to do it.

183
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:29,559
Xiao Yifan's wife and child,

184
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,559
I had them kidnapped too.

185
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,759
Running people over,

186
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:34,879
kidnapping...

187
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:36,879
These are people's lives!

188
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,840
Fang Bing, since when did you get so reckless?

189
00:09:43,399 --> 00:09:44,960
They got in the way of my money first.

190
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,519
President Su.

191
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:52,440
I'm carrying Bing's child.

192
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,240
Can you spare me and the baby?

193
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,879
Spare you?

194
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,080
Then who's going to spare me?
